ARTFULLY SUITED 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Regarding "Artfully Suited," by Mary Rourke (Aug. 27): My trusty calculator 
tells me that it cost $19,436 to dress the nine women you chose to highlight 
women's fall fashions: an average of $2,159.55 per outfit. There is not an 
outfit in there that cannot be duplicated for less than $50 at the Salvation 
Army. I guess those ladies will just have to keep the price tags on to truly 
get their money's worth. 
</P>
<P>
FREDERICK CLEVELAND, Hollywood 
