</P>
<P>
Underweight: 8% : 7% 
</P>
<P>
Actual government figures 
</P>
<P>
Overweight: 22%: 24% 
</P>
<P>
Right weight: 71%: 69% 
</P>
<P>
Underweight: 7% : 7% 
</P>
<P>
What kind of physical activity or sport did you engage in most during the last 
7 days? 
</P>
<P>
