</P>
<P>
Candy: 12% 
</P>
<P>
Pizza: 8% 
</P>
<P>
Cookies: 7% 
</P>
<P>
What's the most important bad habit you have that is hurting your health? 
</P>
<P>
Smoking: 26% 
</P>
<P>
Eating wrong foods: 18% 
</P>
<P>
Eating too much: 15% 
</P>
<P>
Drinking: 9% 
</P>
<P>
Not exercising: 8% 
</P>
<P>
Taking drugs: 2% 
</P>
<P>
No bad habits: 20% 
</P>
</TEXT>
