and reuniting, are planning to marry again. DOUGLAS R. BURROWS; Photo, 
Hollywood dream: Don Johnson, Melanie Griffith, together again. ANACLETO 
RAPPING / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
