</P>
<P>
Bette Davis -- The Oct. 8 obituary of actress Bette Davis stated that she had 
unsuccessfully sought the role of Hedvig in Henrik Ibsen's "The Wild Duck." In 
fact the part became one of her earliest stage triumphs. 
</P>
