Constitution. 
</P>
<P>
</P>
<P>
Expansion of Death Penalty 
</P>
<P>
Also, the death penalty would be expanded to cover more types of killings, and 
juveniles 16 or 17 who commit murder would be subject to life in prison without 
parole. Pretrial proceedings, including jury selection, would be sharply 
