Lodish recovering for UCLA. ; Photo, Mark McGill (19) of UCLA brings down Jeff 
Simoneau of Arizona State after a seven-yard gain. ALBERT DIAZ / Los Angeles 
Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
