<HEADLINE>
<P>
BUSIEST MARKETS FOR SINGLE-FAMILY CONSTRUCTION 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Busiest single-family markets in the nation based on single-family permits 
issued in the first half of 1989. 
</P>
